0x03-sass_scss
# Steps I took to install SASS 

1.I open Ubuntu terminal.

2. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm):
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Exit terminal and reopen it:
   $ exit

4. Verify nvm installation:
   $ nvm --version

5. Install Node.js version 20.16:
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16
   $ node -v

6. Install SASS version 3.7.4:
   $ npm install sass -v 3.7.4

7. Verify SASS installation (optional):
   $ npx sass --version
